translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even though your appearance is like that...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これからの仕事とか考えてるの？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Are you thinking about your future work or something?
"...This person is as spontaneous as ever,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 行き当たりばったりだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: just going wherever the wind takes them."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そういうとこあるのよね……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you have that kind of trait, don't you..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一度やると決めたことだしね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Since I've decided to do it once."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うわ、小っこい癖に無駄に男前……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Wow, even though you're small, you're unnecessarily manly..."
"...Looks like more troubles are about to come."
"Are my sister and those people close?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そりゃもう、十年来の友達ですから」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Of course, they've been friends for over ten years."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香がナギを連れて、カスタムに帰ってきた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shizuka returned to Custom, bringing Nagi along.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぷらっと志津香が現れた。
「なんだ？　志津香が一人で
俺の部屋に来るとは珍しいな」
「ちょっと、相談があるんだけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I have something to talk about... Is it okay?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前が俺に相談とは珍しい……」
「父親のように振る舞ってあげて欲しいの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I want you to act like a father to her."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「別に父親になれとか変な話じゃなくて……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's not like I'm asking you to actually become her father or anything weird..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの子、生まれが生まれでしょ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She has that kind of background, you know.
"To let her experience something like that..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前がそんな素直に頭を下げるなんて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's rare to see you genuinely bow your head like that,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 珍しいもの見られたからな、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so consider this payment for that."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのお代みたいなもんだ」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Just do the same as you do with Reset."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 同じようにしたらいいわよ」
「まあ、そういうことするって
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, just being a little conscious about acting that way is enough."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し意識してくれるだけでいいわ」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh, speak of the devil, you came right away."
